## System GSettings GUI

- Graphical interface for system settings
- Manage appearance, accessibility, and personalization
- Easy access to configuration options

## Security Settings

- User account management
- Password and authentication settings
- System update and patch management
- Firewall and network security controls

## Security Tunneling Protocol

- Secure communication channels for remote access
- Support for VPN and encrypted tunnels
- Integration with system authentication

## Subprocess & Processor Management (Termux)

- Utilities for managing and running subprocesses in Termux terminal
- Process monitoring and control tools
- Support for executing background and foreground tasks
- Integration with Termux process utilities (ps, top, kill, etc.)

## Windows 98 Virtual Machine Overlay with Full GUI

- Emulated Windows 98 environment with complete graphical interface
- Full-featured desktop, start menu, and taskbar
- Support for running legacy Windows 98 applications
- Seamless integration with host system for file and network access
